scale_sd.Rd

Centers and scales each column by standard deviation (sd) or to the interval (0, 1).

scale_sd(data)

scale_01(data)

Arguments

data

Numeric matrix or data.frame of the observations.

Examples

scale_sd(data = wine[, 2:6])
